caption: An empty skateboard glides smoothly across the expansive, sunlit parking lot. The wheels create a soft, rhythmic sound as they roll over the concrete surface. As it moves, the skateboard casts a long shadow, stretching across the ground, hinting at the late afternoon sun. The scene is calm and serene, with the skateboard continuing its journey across the open space, undisturbed by any obstacles.
